      "content": "that 17 second gap is exactly what i was looking for. if the telemetry was being manipulated in real-time like that, it suggests a coordinated effort to hide the visual of the structure. if they were overwriting the camera memory too, they were clearly trying to sanitize the record before it even reached earth. what kind of specific data or \"fluctuations\" are we talking about in the readings after the gap? does the telemetry imply they were reacting to something they shouldn't have seen?",
